LineNo: 11165804,

Narrator: In the fertile fields of Qalus, the...
en


In the fertile fields of Qalus, the Cantuavo vineyards were among the oldest in Rizia.

LineNo: 11165906,

Narrator: They were run by a revered winemaki...
en


They were run by a revered winemaking family now in their fifth generation, who had long ago been awarded noble status for the fine wines they provided the kingdom.

LineNo: 11166008,

Narrator: Tonight, they had invited my family...
en


Tonight, they had invited my family and council over for the ceremonial uncorking of their latest vintage, "Romus the Red". Bottled on my coronation day, it was now ready for drinking.

LineNo: 11166110,

Narrator: I wished I was in more of a celebra...
en


I wished I was in more of a celebratory mood.

LineNo: 11166490,

Narrator: As if that weren't enough, tensions...
en


As if that weren't enough, tensions with Pales were higher than ever. We were still awaiting the arbitration results.

LineNo: 11166592,

Narrator: In the meantime, the Rizian navy re...
en


In the meantime, the Rizian navy remained deployed around the Aureus field, despite the international community's growing concern.

LineNo: 11166972,

Narrator: And gas tankers were venturing off...
en


And gas tankers were venturing off from Monqiz, Porte Drazon, and Fort Ales to Rumburg to fulfill our natural gas exports every single day.

LineNo: 11167352,

Narrator: For now, all I had to do was open a...
en


For now, all I had to do was open a wine bottle. But even that was politicized. Hugo had stressed the importance of keeping the Cantuavo family loyal to our house.

LineNo: 11167454,

Narrator: Wehlen's announcement at the AN had...
en


Wehlen's announcement at the AN had plunged the country into panic. I was besieged by demands to take action to get Zille back.

LineNo: 11167556,

Narrator: It wouldn't be easy. My decision to...
en


It wouldn't be easy. My decision to open a gold mine in the heart of Rizian wine country had angered many in the Valenqiris nobility, the Cantuavos foremost among them.

LineNo: 11167936,

Narrator: Our motorcade rolled up to the vine...
en


Our motorcade rolled up to the vineyard entrance, where a festival tent decorated in the blue, white and gold of the Rizian flag had been set up.

LineNo: 11168038,

Narrator: After a thorough security sweep, my...
en


After a thorough security sweep, my mother Estela, Vina, Hugo and I proceeded to our table. Pabel smoothly approached and poured us glasses of sparkling water.

LineNo: 11168140,

Pabel Adria: I had the pleasure of supervising...
en


"I had the pleasure of supervising the pre-tasting with the vineyard staff. I must say, the family has truly outdone themselves this time."

LineNo: 11168266,

Player_Romus: How much of it do I have to drink?
en


"How much of it do I have to drink?"

LineNo: 11168638,

Player_Romus: How splendid. I can't wait.
en


"How splendid. I can't wait."

LineNo: 11168740,

Player_Romus: So you're drunk already, Pabel?
en


"So you're drunk already, Pabel?"

LineNo: 11168842,

Player_Romus: It's named after me. It had better...
en


"It's named after me. It had better be good."

LineNo: 11168944,

Pabel Adria: Only a small sip when the first bo...
en


"Only a small sip when the first bottle is uncorked, Your Majesty. I've arranged for a substitute to be served to you the rest of the time."

LineNo: 11169046,

Pabel Adria: I honestly think you'll love it. I...
en


"I honestly think you'll love it. It's light on the palate at first, but it has hidden depths."

LineNo: 11169426,

Narrator: Pabel cracked a smile.
en


Pabel cracked a smile.

LineNo: 11169528,

Pabel Adria: We spit it out during the tasting,...
en


"We spit it out during the tasting, Your Majesty. Unfortunately."

LineNo: 11169630,

Narrator: Pabel's expression didn't change.
en


Pabel's expression didn't change.

LineNo: 11169732,

Pabel Adria: Never, Your Majesty. We only taste...
en


"Never, Your Majesty. We only taste enough to judge the wine's character."

LineNo: 11170112,

Pabel Adria: I hope you'll enjoy it. But let me...
en


"I hope you'll enjoy it. But let me know immediately if you don't, and I'll find one that's more to your liking."

LineNo: 11170214,

Narrator: All three were dressed more festive...
en


All three were dressed more festively than the simple formalwear they wore to council meetings, but Lucita's slinky, intricately beaded yellow gown was particularly eye-catching.

LineNo: 11170316,

Estela Toras: Oh, my. The mountains of Montaklar...
en


"Oh, my. The mountains of Montaklar are on full display tonight."

LineNo: 11170442,

Narrator: My mother turned to me and muttered...
en


My mother turned to me and muttered under her breath.

LineNo: 11170544,

Player_Romus: And how!
en


"And how!"

LineNo: 11170646,

Player_Romus: Honestly, Mother. I'll have you ki...
en


"Honestly, Mother. I'll have you kicked out if you insist on demeaning my councilor like that."

LineNo: 11170748,

Player_Romus: You're just jealous that for once,...
en


"You're just jealous that for once, someone else's outfit is better than yours."

LineNo: 11170850,

Player_Romus: Mountains? What are you talking ab...
en


"Mountains? What are you talking about?"

LineNo: 11170952,

Narrator: Vina nodded in agreement, but there...
en


Vina nodded in agreement, but there was a wariness in her eyes.

LineNo: 11171054,

Narrator: Vina rolled her eyes in disgust.
en


Vina rolled her eyes in disgust.

LineNo: 11171156,

Vina Toras: I still don't understand what we'r...
en


"I still don't understand what we're doing here. Especially with all that's been going on."

LineNo: 11171536,

Narrator: Vina nodded in agreement.
en


Vina nodded in agreement.

LineNo: 11171638,

Narrator: Vina stifled a giggle.
en


Vina stifled a giggle.

LineNo: 11171740,

Narrator: Vina rolled her eyes and ran a fing...
en


Vina rolled her eyes and ran a finger along the rim of her glass.

LineNo: 11171842,

Hugo Toras: Politics, Your Highness. In case o...
en


"Politics, Your Highness. In case our foreign situation escalates, we'll require the support of House Toras and our home province more than ever."

LineNo: 11171984,

Player_Romus: Yes, we must keep attending functi...
en


"Yes, we must keep attending functions as usual. As the royal family, we've got the spirit of Rizia to uphold."

LineNo: 11172086,

Player_Romus: Vina has a point. President Smolak...
en


"Vina has a point. President Smolak and I haven't exchanged a word since Zille. Shouldn't I make it my priority to talk to him?"

LineNo: 11172188,

Player_Romus: Come to think of it, won't the Val...
en


"Come to think of it, won't the Valenqiris nobility want me skinned alive for taking the side of a Malenyevist at the AN?"

LineNo: 11172838,

Vina Toras: A Valgslandian Socialist, Father,...
en


"A Valgslandian Socialist, Father, There's a difference."

LineNo: 11172940,

Hugo Toras: Not to our relations, Your Highnes...
en


"Not to our relations, Your Highness."

LineNo: 11173042,

Hugo Toras: Many members of our house still ha...
en


"Many members of our house still have Valgish blood. Of course they despise the direction taken by the old empire, but some sympathy might remain."

LineNo: 11173144,

Hugo Toras: A predicament, yes. But not a cris...
en


"A predicament, yes. But not a crisis."

LineNo: 11173246,

Hugo Toras: Mr. Esquibel has already set up th...
en


"Mr. Esquibel has already set up the meeting, Your Majesty. He has a team putting together our case as we speak."

LineNo: 11173348,

Hugo Toras: For now, it's important we reassur...
en


"For now, it's important we reassure our wealthiest citizens that the situation will not affect their assets."

LineNo: 11173450,

Hugo Toras: Precisely, Your Majesty.
en


"Precisely, Your Majesty."

LineNo: 11173552,

Hugo Toras: In this case, it's especially impo...
en


"In this case, it's especially important for our wealthiest citizens to be reassured that their assets will remain stable."

LineNo: 11173654,

Hugo Toras: All you have to do is reassure the...
en


"All you have to do is reassure them that their assets will remain stable."

LineNo: 11173756,

Narrator: Pabel lowered his voice.
en


Pabel lowered his voice.

LineNo: 11173858,

Hugo Toras: That sounds perfect, Mr. Adria. Bu...
en


"That sounds perfect, Mr. Adria. But please stick to conservative pours for His Majesty. It's unbecoming of a king to get intoxicated at these functions."

LineNo: 11173960,

Hugo Toras: A prudent decision, Mr. Adria. It'...
en


"A prudent decision, Mr. Adria. It's unbecoming of a king to get intoxicated at these functions."

LineNo: 11174062,

Hugo Toras: Very prudent, Mr. Adria. One would...
en


"Very prudent, Mr. Adria. One wouldn't want to become too intoxicated at such an important function."

LineNo: 11174164,

Narrator: Lucita, Elena and Laurento walked p...
en


Lucita, Elena and Laurento walked past us and were seated at the table next to ours.

LineNo: 11174266,

Pabel Adria: Honestly, it's a good fit for you....
en


"Honestly, it's a good fit for you. It's light on the palate at first, but it has hidden depths."

LineNo: 11174646,

Pabel Adria: I hope you'll enjoy it. But let me...
en


"I hope you'll enjoy it. But let me know immediately if you don't, and I'll find one that's more to your liking."

LineNo: 11174748,

Narrator: My mother smiled wryly.
en


My mother smiled wryly.

LineNo: 11174850,

Estela Toras: Hidden depths indeed.
en


"Hidden depths indeed."

LineNo: 11174952,

Narrator: The rest of the attendees began fil...
en


The rest of the attendees began filing in. It was a small, elite crowd, comprising barons and baronesses, viscounts and CEOs from around the region.

LineNo: 11175054,

Narrator: They bowed as they passed my table....
en


They bowed as they passed my table. Some had fear in their eyes.

LineNo: 11175426,

Player_Romus: Do you think they're concerned abo...
en


"Do you think they're concerned about the naval standoff in the Antacean?"

LineNo: 11175528,

Hugo Toras: That and President Smolak's announ...
en


"That and President Smolak's announcement, of course."

LineNo: 11175630,

Hugo Toras: But they're not a hard group to pl...
en


"But they're not a hard group to please. All you have to do is reassure them that their assets will remain stable."

LineNo: 11176010,

Narrator: They bowed as they passed my table,...
en


They bowed as they passed my table, but some of their smiles seemed ungenuine. I thought I heard someone whisper "Sord-lover".

LineNo: 11176112,

Narrator: Each of them bowed as they passed m...
en


Each of them bowed as they passed my table.

LineNo: 11176214,

Narrator: Estela flashed me a look of warning...
en


Estela flashed me a look of warning.

LineNo: 11176316,

Estela Toras: There's no pleasing these people,...
en


"There's no pleasing these people, darling. Better to ignore them."

LineNo: 11176418,

Narrator: They bowed as they passed my table,...
en


They bowed as they passed my table, but some of their smiles seemed ungenuine. I thought I heard someone whisper "Party Prince".

LineNo: 11177076,

Hugo Toras: You still command their respect af...
en


"You still command their respect after your reign as Duke of Valenqiris. A good start."

LineNo: 11177178,

Narrator: After everyone had settled in, the...
en


After everyone had settled in, the head of the winery gave a short opening greeting, then welcomed me onto the stage.

LineNo: 11177280,

Narrator: I stepped behind the microphone. A...
en


I stepped behind the microphone. A magnum-sized bottle of Romus the Red stood on the table behind me.

LineNo: 11177398,

Player_Romus: Ladies and gentlemen.
en


"Ladies and gentlemen."

LineNo: 11177516,

Player_Romus: My esteemed fellow nobles.
en


"My esteemed fellow nobles."

LineNo: 11177634,

Player_Romus: Great citizens of Valenqiris.
en


"Great citizens of Valenqiris."

LineNo: 11177752,

Player_Romus: We are gathered here to celebrate...
en


"We are gathered here to celebrate the fruits of this land. Our land."

LineNo: 11177870,

Player_Romus: I know they're not happy about my...
en


"I know they're not happy about my dealings with Sordland."

LineNo: 11178242,

Hugo Toras: They don't hold the Republic or it...
en


"They don't hold the Republic or its citizens in particularly high regard, no."

LineNo: 11178344,

Hugo Toras: But more pressing is Wehlen's anno...
en


"But more pressing is Wehlen's announcement regarding Zille. You have to reassure them that their assets will remain stable."

LineNo: 11178446,

Player_Romus: I am honored to lend my name to th...
en


"I am honored to lend my name to this exceptional creation, produced by the best winemakers in the country -- no, the world."

LineNo: 11178564,

Player_Romus: Today, we raise our glasses to our...
en


"Today, we raise our glasses to our fine province, the foundation upon which this kingdom stands."

LineNo: 11178674,

Player_Romus: This wine will only grow better ov...
en


"This wine will only grow better over time. Just like the reign of the king it is named after."

LineNo: 11178792,

Player_Romus: The wines of this vineyard have al...
en


"The wines of this vineyard have always delighted our palates in times of joy and calmed our nerves in times of sorrow."

LineNo: 11179188,

Player_Romus: This wine will inspire reverence f...
en


"This wine will inspire reverence for the venerable House Toras and the nation of Rizia in anyone whose lips it touches. Yes, even Sords."

LineNo: 11179290,

Player_Romus: This wine will inspire reverence f...
en


"This wine will inspire reverence for the venerable House Toras and the nation of Rizia in anyone whose lips it touches."

LineNo: 11179408,

Narrator: I heard a few chuckles.
en


I heard a few chuckles.

LineNo: 11179526,

Player_Romus: I have listened to my people. I kn...
en


"I have listened to my people. I know some of you have doubts about our kingdom's stability."

LineNo: 11179652,

Player_Romus: I am heartened that so many of you...
en


"I am heartened that so many of you have come here to celebrate tonight. Especially in the wake of recent events."

LineNo: 11179778,

Player_Romus: Yes, there are those who seek to w...
en


"Yes, there are those who seek to weaken our ancient monarchy. To claim our riches for their own."

LineNo: 11179904,

Player_Romus: Change is coming to Rizia. But tha...
en


"Change is coming to Rizia. But that need not be a bad thing."

LineNo: 11180022,

Player_Romus: I am but an instrument of God's wi...
en


"I am but an instrument of God's will. But I know the Lord has great plans for Rizia."

LineNo: 11180418,

Player_Romus: We should not be scared to look ou...
en


"We should not be scared to look outwards. To rekindle our international friendships."

LineNo: 11180552,

Player_Romus: We should not hesitate to look to...
en


"We should not hesitate to look to our fellow royal houses for support."

LineNo: 11180670,

Player_Romus: Now, more than ever, we must defen...
en


"Now, more than ever, we must defend our traditions and our way of life."

LineNo: 11180788,

Player_Romus: I am confident that with your help...
en


"I am confident that with your help, Rizia will become stronger than ever."

LineNo: 11181994,

Player_Romus: Our brothers and sisters in Morell...
en


"Our brothers and sisters in Morella, for example."

LineNo: 11182096,

Player_Romus: Our Wruhecist brethren in Derdia,...
en


"Our Wruhecist brethren in Derdia, for example."

LineNo: 11182198,

Player_Romus: Our Valgish cousins have not forgo...
en


"Our Valgish cousins have not forgotten us. And we have not forgotten them."

LineNo: 11182300,

Player_Romus: Lespia's politics may greatly diff...
en


"Lespia's politics may greatly differ from ours, but they are still our neighbor."

LineNo: 11182402,

Player_Romus: Like that which my grandmother for...
en


"Like that which my grandmother formed with the Kingdom of Sordland."

LineNo: 11182504,

Player_Romus: The support of Rumburg and our fel...
en


"The support of Rumburg and our fellow monarchies in GRACE will be invaluable."

LineNo: 11182606,

Player_Romus: The Azaros' military and industria...
en


"The Azaros' military and industrial prowess has served our kingdom well in the past, and it will in the future."

LineNo: 11182708,

Player_Romus: We may have a turbulent past with...
en


"We may have a turbulent past with the Sazons, but we cannot ignore their compassion for commoners and patronage of arts and education."

LineNo: 11182810,

Narrator: Lucita applauded, surprise and grat...
en


Lucita applauded, surprise and gratitude spreading across her face. She was the only one clapping.

LineNo: 11182928,

Narrator: Vina quietly applauded from her sea...
en


Vina quietly applauded from her seat. She was the only one.

LineNo: 11183046,

Player_Romus: The Toras, Azaro and Sazon familie...
en


"The Toras, Azaro and Sazon families are all integral to Rizian prosperity. By uniting, we will stay strong."

LineNo: 11183148,

Narrator: There was a round of polite applaus...
en


There was a round of polite applause. I couldn't tell what my audience was thinking.

LineNo: 11183266,

Player_Romus: I look at this beautiful bottle of...
en


"I look at this beautiful bottle of wine and dream of a day when all Rizians are able to experience such luxury."

LineNo: 11183368,

Player_Romus: True nobility comes not from any b...
en


"True nobility comes not from any birthright, but from choosing to share one's wealth."

LineNo: 11183470,

Player_Romus: It is time for us to accept one an...
en


"It is time for us to accept one another's differences, regardless of status or nationality."

LineNo: 11183572,

Player_Romus: I know one thing for certain. By t...
en


"I know one thing for certain. By this time next year, we'll be raising a glass of Romus the Red to a reunited Rizia."

LineNo: 11183674,

Narrator: I heard a few polite claps.
en


I heard a few polite claps.

LineNo: 11183792,

Player_Romus: That's all the applause I get? I a...
en


"That's all the applause I get? I am your king!"

LineNo: 11183894,

Player_Romus: I promise that if we open ourselve...
en


"I promise that if we open ourselves to new alliances, untold prosperity will be our reward."

LineNo: 11183996,

Narrator: The crowd hurriedly erupted into lo...
en


The crowd hurriedly erupted into loud cheers. A representative of the winery handed me a ceremonial corkscrew and a glass.

LineNo: 11184122,

Narrator: I heard cheers as a representative...
en


I heard cheers as a representative of the winery handed me a ceremonial corkscrew and a glass.

LineNo: 11184248,

Player_Romus: It may take time and we may have t...
en


"It may take time and we may have to make sacrifices. But we will take back our rightful territory."

LineNo: 11184350,

Player_Romus: With Valenqiris by my side, Rizia...
en


"With Valenqiris by my side, Rizia will be whole again."

LineNo: 11184452,

Player_Romus: By this time next year, we'll be r...
en


"By this time next year, we'll be raising a glass of Romus the Red to a reunited Rizia."

LineNo: 11184554,

Player_Romus_Italic: I used the corkscrew to open the wi...
en


I used the corkscrew to open the wine bottle.

LineNo: 11184560,

Player_Romus_Italic: I used the corkscrew to open the wi...
Menu Text en


Uncork the wine.

LineNo: 11184662,

Player_Romus: A proso!
en


"A proso!"

Player_Romus: Glovurius axa Rizia!
en


"Glovurius axa Rizia!"

LineNo: 11184866,

Player_Romus: To House Toras!
en


"To House Toras!"

LineNo: 11184968,

Player_Romus: I'd like to invite Princess Vina t...
en


"I'd like to invite Princess Vina to do the honors."

LineNo: 11185076,

Player_Romus: Hugo Toras, a true man of Valenqir...
en


"Hugo Toras, a true man of Valenqiris, will open the bottle in my stead."

LineNo: 11185184,

Player_Romus: As a symbol of unity, Duchess Luci...
en


"As a symbol of unity, Duchess Lucita of House Azaro will uncork the first bottle."

LineNo: 11185292,

Narrator: Vina blushed furiously as she got o...
en


Vina blushed furiously as she got on stage. An assistant quickly procured a second glass.

LineNo: 11185394,

Narrator: With a look of pleasant surprise, H...
en


With a look of pleasant surprise, Hugo got on stage. An assistant quickly procured two glasses.

LineNo: 11185496,

Narrator: With a stunned yet delighted expres...
en


With a stunned yet delighted expression, Lucita took the stage. An assistant quickly procured two glasses.

LineNo: 11185598,

Narrator: My daughter opened the bottle and p...
en


My daughter opened the bottle and poured us each a small amount.

LineNo: 11185724,

Narrator: My uncle opened the bottle and pour...
en


My uncle opened the bottle and poured us each a small amount.

LineNo: 11185850,

Narrator: My war councilor opened the bottle...
en


My war councilor opened the bottle and poured us each a small amount.

LineNo: 11185976,

Player_Romus: A proso!
en


"A proso!"

LineNo: 11186078,

Player_Romus: Glovurius axa Rizia!
en


"Glovurius axa Rizia!"

LineNo: 11186180,

Player_Romus: To House Toras!
en


"To House Toras!"

LineNo: 11186282,

Player_Romus_Italic: We clinked glasses and drank.
en


We clinked glasses and drank.

LineNo: 11186288,

Player_Romus_Italic: We clinked glasses and drank.
Menu Text en


Drink.

en


I raised my glass towards the audience and drank.

LineNo: 11186396,

Player_Romus_Italic: I raised my glass towards the audie...
Menu Text en


Drink.

LineNo: 11186776,

Narrator: It was delicious. A light, refreshi...
en


It was delicious. A light, refreshing taste gradually developed into a darker and more complex finish.

LineNo: 11186878,

Narrator: I had to admit it was delicious. A...
en


I had to admit it was delicious. A light, refreshing taste gradually developed into a darker and more complex finish.

LineNo: 11188102,

Player_Romus: As the most privileged province in...
en


"As the most privileged province in Rizia, Valenqiris has a duty to lead the way forward."

LineNo: 11188228,

Player_Romus: I am a proud son of Valenqiris. An...
en


"I am a proud son of Valenqiris. And I assure you that my home province will always come first for me."

LineNo: 11188354,

Player_Romus: We must not forget that Valenqiris...
en


"We must not forget that Valenqiris is not an island."

LineNo: 11188472,

Player_Romus: He chose my family to guide this c...
en


"He chose my family to guide this country. And I will not let Him or you down."

LineNo: 11188598,

Player_Romus: Yet we should not be scared to loo...
en


"Yet we should not be scared to look outwards. To rekindle our international friendships."

LineNo: 11188732,

Player_Romus: Yet we should not hesitate to look...
en


"Yet we should not hesitate to look to our fellow royal houses for support."

LineNo: 11188850,

Player_Romus: But we can no longer ignore the pl...
en


"But we can no longer ignore the plight of those less fortunate than us."

LineNo: 11188976,

Player_Romus: No longer can we ignore the plight...
en


"No longer can we ignore the plight of those less fortunate than us."

LineNo: 11189102,

Player_Romus: I know that as King, I have tested...
en


"I know that as King, I have tested your loyalty at times. But rest assured, your continued faith in me and in House Toras will be richly rewarded."

LineNo: 11189204,

Narrator: The crowd applauded somewhat tepidl...
en


The crowd applauded somewhat tepidly.

LineNo: 11189330,

Player_Romus: I swore at my coronation that I wo...
en


"I swore at my coronation that I would make Rizia whole again. And I intend to keep that promise."

LineNo: 11189702,

Player_Romus: Our enemies' blood will flow as re...
en


"Our enemies' blood will flow as red as this wine, and our revenge will taste as sweet."

LineNo: 11189804,

Narrator: The crowd applauded with gusto. Vin...
en


The crowd applauded with gusto. Vina had a skeptical look on her face.

LineNo: 11189922,

Narrator: The crowd applauded with gusto. Hug...
en


The crowd applauded with gusto. Hugo had a relieved look on his face.

LineNo: 11190040,

Player_Romus: I swore at my coronation that I wo...
en


"I swore at my coronation that I would make Rizia whole again. And with Valenqiris by my side, I will keep that promise."

LineNo: 11190420,

Player_Romus: When we reclaim Zille, I will make...
en


"When we reclaim Zille, I will make sure that we nobles are not the only ones to reap the benefits."

LineNo: 11190522,

Narrator: The attendees applauded somewhat te...
en


The attendees applauded somewhat tepidly.

LineNo: 11190648,

Narrator: The attendees applauded slightly mo...
en


The attendees applauded slightly more loudly.

LineNo: 11190774,

Player_Romus: But you're not here to listen to m...
en


"But you're not here to listen to me. You're here to drink wine."

LineNo: 11190876,

Player_Romus: For now, we will bear witness to t...
en


"For now, we will bear witness to the miracles that the Cantuavo family have worked with the humble grape."

LineNo: 11190978,

Player_Romus: Tonight, let us remind ourselves h...
en


"Tonight, let us remind ourselves how much Rizia still has to celebrate!"

LineNo: 11191080,

Narrator: There was a final round of applause...
